import numpy as np
import pandas as pd

t = np.arange(0., 5., 0.2)
plt.title("라인 플롯에서 여러개의 선 그리기")
plt.plot(t, t, 'r--', t, 0.5 * t**2, 'bs:', t, 0.2 * t**3, 'g^-')
plt.show()

X = np.linspace(-np.pi, np.pi, 256)
C, S = np.cos(X), np.sin(X)

plt.plot(X, S, ls=":", label="sine")

plt.show()

import matplotlib as mpl
import matplotlib.pylab as plt

y = [2, 3, 1]
x = np.arange(len(y))
xlabel = ['가', '나', '다']
plt.title("Bar Chart")
plt.bar(x, y) # bar를 넣으면 bar그래프, barh넣으면 가로로 bar그래프(항아리그래프, 하나를 마이너스값을 넣어야 함)
plt.xticks(x, xlabel)
plt.yticks(sorted(y))
plt.xlabel("가나다")
plt.ylabel("빈도 수")
plt.show()

plt.axis('equal')

labels = ['개구리', '돼지', '개', '통나무']
sizes = [15, 30, 45, 10]
colors = ['yellowgreen', 'gold', 'lightskyblue', 'lightcoral']
explode = (0, 0.1, 0, 0)
plt.title("Pie Chart")
plt.pie(sizes, explode=explode, labels=labels, colors=colors,
        autopct='%1.1f%%', shadow=True, startangle=90)
plt.axis('equal')
plt.show()
